(1, 'What is CLV in number form?', '150', '165', '155', '145', '155', 'C is 100, L is 50, and V is 5. Adding them gives 155.', 'Medium'),
(1, 'What is 32 in Roman numeral form?', 'XLII', 'XXX', 'XXXII', 'XXII', 'XXXII', '32 is written as XXXII because XXX is 30 and II is 2.', 'Medium'),
(1, 'What is 60 in Roman numeral form?', 'XL', 'LX', 'XC', 'L', 'LX', 'L means 50 and X means 10. Together, LX equals 60.', 'Medium'),
