(1, 'Jonathan sold 250 apples last week. This week he sold 70 fewer. How many apples did he sell in two weeks?', '320 apples', '450 apples', '430 apples', '500 apples', '430 apples', 'This week he sold 180 apples. Adding both weeks gives 430 apples.', 'Medium'),
