(1, 'What property is shown: (7 Ã— 9) Ã— 8 = 7 Ã— (9 Ã— 8)?', 'Commutative property', 'Zero property', 'Associative property of multiplication', 'Identity property', 'Associative property of multiplication', 'The associative property shows that changing how numbers are grouped does not change the product.', 'Medium'),
(1, 'What property is shown: 7 Ã— 1 = 7?', 'Commutative property', 'Associative property', 'Identity property of multiplication', 'Zero property', 'Identity property of multiplication', 'Multiplying any number by 1 keeps the number the same.', 'Medium'),
(1, 'What property is shown: 8 Ã— 0 = 0?', 'Associative property', 'Zero property of multiplication', 'Commutative property', 'Identity property', 'Zero property of multiplication', 'Any number multiplied by zero equals zero.', 'Medium'),
