(1, 'Teacher Koro asked her class to bring doughnuts. Nagisa brought 5 boxes and Kaede brought 3 boxes. Each box has 6 doughnuts. How many doughnuts did they bring together?', '36 doughnuts', '54 doughnuts', '48 doughnuts', '42 doughnuts', '48 doughnuts', 'There are 8 boxes in total. Each box has 6 doughnuts, so 8 times 6 equals 48.', 'Medium'),
