(3, 'What happens to water when it gets too cold?', 'It becomes gas', 'It turns into ice', 'It gets hotter', 'It disappears', 'It turns into ice', 'Cold water freezes into ice.', 'Medium'),
(3, 'What happens to ocean water when it gets too hot?', 'It turns into rock', 'It stays the same', 'It becomes ice', 'It turns into water vapor', 'It turns into water vapor', 'Hot water changes into gas called water vapor.', 'Medium'),
