(3, 'What are feather-like clouds called?', 'Nimbus clouds', 'Stratus clouds', 'Cirrus clouds', 'Cumulus clouds', 'Cirrus clouds', 'Cirrus clouds look thin and feathery.', 'Medium'),
(3, 'What are clouds that are small and look like cotton balls?', 'Cirrus clouds', 'Stratus clouds', 'Nimbus clouds', 'Cumulus clouds', 'Stratus clouds', 'Stratus clouds appear in small patches.', 'Medium'),
